Description: Prophyles is reinventing Contact Management with Contacts-as-a-Service (CaaS)
Full Description: Prophyles is reinventing Contact Management by pioneering a new category coined as Contacts-as-a-Service (CaaS).   Prophyles is solving the lingering problems in contact management related to data integrity, accuracy, synchronization, up-to-date, and privacy.  All current vendors, from low-end address books to high-end CRMs, use a centralized database which causes silos which are the main source of the problems.  Prophyles took a unique and contrarian approach by using a decentralized and distributed database in a peer-to-peer network in which profiles are connected using "Smart Contracts" in a blockchain - which is the core of our patent. Prophyles provides your entire digital footprint and those of your contacts, without ever compromising your or their privacy, and without ever being outdated since all Personal Information is constantly updated from the cloud onto your or their device, just like updates of mobile apps.  Prophyles offers you the most comprehensive and protected profile; reduces the probability of identity theft; connects you easily and safely with others through customizable digital cards that represent your different personas which prevent hackers, spammers, or even online predators from preying on your children; leverages your social network by capitalizing on the strength of your weak ties to get you qualified referrals; gets the latest scoop from social media about your contacts; finds people near you; records your daily events in a personalized diary; organizes your ideas in a customized journal; generates flavors of your resumes that are fed to job boards; completes online forms through AI-empowered APIs for you so that you don’t have to, etc. In short, Prophyles is your digital footprint in a truly connected and more secured new online world.

Full Description: Tooktake is a simple dosage reminder system that helps consumers track whether or not they took their prescriptions, supplements, and over-the-counter medications. Medication non-adherence, or failure to take medication as directed, affects two-thirds of the population worldwide, with 70% of prescriptions taken incorrectly or not at all. Medication non-adherence results in 125,000 preventable deaths each year and costs $300 billion in avoidable healthcare costs, as well as lost pharmaceutical revenue. The main reason for non-adherence is that people simply forget to take their medication and then compensate by either over or under-dosing. Tooktake solves this problem by letting consumers know at a glance if they took or still need to take their medication!

Description: DecentraX is building a blockchain & DEX based off of custom hardware technology.
Full Description: DecentraX is building a blockchain & DEX based off of custom hardware technology. The DecentraX (DCX) blockchain is being built from the ground up by designing the proprietary hardware that runs the network around blockchain needs. To-date blockchains are built on top of existing hardware that was not necessarily designed to effectively operate for this industry. Minmaster Chips are designed from the ground up around processing hashing algorithms, to effectively allow for increased Transactions Per Second (TPS). The goal for the DCX team will be to meet and exceed 1,000,000 TPS on the DCX Network. The blockchain will grow out with each new project that is adopted into the DCX Network, starting with a Decentralized Exchange (DEX) that will aim to resolve ease-of-use and liquidity problems seen with the options currently available to the market. DCX will act as the gas of the exchange, as every swap that occurs will be paid for in DCX. The DecentraX team believes that DEX trading is the future and will free projects and investors from the chains seen with centralized exchanges.
Headquarters Regions: Western US

Description: Pause Commercials generates revenue for publishers with AVoD or SVoD business models simply by pressing the pause button.
Full Description: In addition to pre, mid, and post-roll ads, Pause Commercials, or “PUCs”, creates an incremental opportunity for video & display inventory when viewers activate the pause button on their remote control.  In layman’s terms, you’re watching a streaming service, pause the device, and a video or display ad appears.  Because our pause-ads complement traditional pre, mid, and post roll options, there is potential for broader reach and engagement for advertisers as well as increased earnings for publishers. As of July 2020, the USPTO issued PUCs the patent to the pause-ad method in OTT.  Licensing is currently available for publishers and distributors who already have pause-ad capability, and our proprietary technology, including pre-, mid-, post roll, and pause-ads, is available to platforms who don’t have pause-ad capability.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
